---
/* src/components/sheer-elegance/Technical.astro */
---

<section class="bg-[#0e0e0e] py-32 px-8 border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
      <div>
        <span class="text-[#dcef42] font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] font-black tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] uppercase mb-4 block italic">// Características Elite</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white leading-tight">
          Ingeniería para el <br/>confort <span class="text-[#dcef42] italic">moderno.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <div class="group bg-[#131313] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:border-[#dcef42]/30 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#dcef42]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#dcef42] group-hover:bg-[#dcef42] group-hover:text-[#131313] transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">brightness_medium</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white mb-4">Control Dinámico</h4>
        <p class="text-white/70 font-['Inter'] leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Ajuste preciso de la entrada de luz con solo un movimiento, permitiendo transiciones suaves entre luz y sombra. Ideal para adaptarse a los constantes cambios climáticos de la región.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-[#131313] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:border-[#dcef42]/30 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#dcef42]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#dcef42] group-hover:bg-[#dcef42] group-hover:text-[#131313] transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shield</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white mb-4">Protección UV</h4>
        <p class="text-white/70 font-['Inter'] leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Proteja sus muebles, pisos y decoración de la decoloración solar, sin sacrificar la hermosa vista al exterior y los paisajes característicos de la Sabana Centro.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group bg-[#131313] border border-white/5 p-10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:border-[#dcef42]/30 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#dcef42]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#dcef42] group-hover:bg-[#dcef42] group-hover:text-[#131313] transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">palette</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white mb-4">Diseño Sofisticado</h4>
        <p class="text-white/70 font-['Inter'] leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Disponibles en una amplia gama de texturas y tonalidades que se integran a cualquier estilo decorativo. Llevamos nuestro catálogo de muestras físicas directamente a tu domicilio.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>